## 4. Critical Architecture Mandates

*   **JS-Driven UI:** Move away from the monolithic HTML. Use templates and render functions.
*   **Proxy Everything:** All MLB/Savant calls **MUST** go through `/api/mlb` or `/api/savant`.
*   **No Hardcoding:** Remove the static Shohei Ohtani block; render all profiles from data.

---

## 5. Data Architecture & Proxy Routing
*   **MLB API:** `/api/mlb?path=/people/{id}`
*   **Savant API:** `/api/savant?endpoint=statcast_leaderboard`

---

## 6. Analytics Philosophy & Percentile Engine
*   **Directional Logic:** Ensure K%, Chase%, and Whiff% percentiles are inverted (Lower = Better).
*   **Clamping:** All percentiles should be clamped between 1 and 99.

---

## 7. UI / Visual System Rules (STRICT SPEC)

### The Percentile Row Template
```html
<template id="tpl-pct-row">
  <div class="pct-row">
    <div class="pct-label"></div>
    <div class="pct-track">
      <div class="pct-midpoint"></div> <!-- Vertical line at 50% -->
      <div class="pct-fill"></div>
      <div class="pct-bubble"></div> <!-- Sits on fill edge -->
    </div>
    <div class="pct-raw"></div>
  </div>
</template>
```

